Jennifer Garner, 50, shared a smiley Instagram clip to her 13.4 million followers in which she filmed herself in front of the Golden Gate Bridge in San Francisco and beamed as her brunette hair blew in the wind.The post is Jennifer’s first selfie since her ex-husband Ben Affleck married Jennifer Lopez in a second ceremony last weekend. Many fans took to the comments to praise the Pearl Harbor star. Chana described her as "wholesome" while Dani said Jennifer is "Always so beautiful". JLo and Ben are currently enjoying their second honeymoon in Italy.  In photographs captured on Thursday the loved-up couple were spotted shopping in Milan and JLo looked cool in matching white trousers, crop top and fedora.Ben looked casual in blue jeans and a shirt as he walked hand-in-hand with his new wife.